RCW 28A.500.040

Distribution of funds.

Local effort assistance funds shall be distributed to qualifying districts as follows:(1) Thirty percent in April;(2) Twenty-three percent in May;(3) Two percent in June;(4) Seventeen percent in August;(5) Nine percent in October;(6) Seventeen percent in November; and(7) Two percent in December.

